Cell["\<\
Repeated application of the annihilation operator eventually takes any Fock \
state to the vacuum, and one more application yields the zero vector.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9695614167540407`*^9, 3.9714510249825306`*^9},
 CellID->191412410,ExpressionUUID->"50fdade9-dc23-46d1-877d-730988d0cbd1"],

