   RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", " ", 
    RowBox[{"FockState", "[", "0", "]"}]}], "+", 
   RowBox[{"\[Beta]", " ", 
    RowBox[{"FockState", "[", "1", "]"}]}]}]}]], "ExerciseInput",
 CellLabel->"In[119]:=",
 CellID->47763380,ExpressionUUID->"ae4cf41e-2910-4a41-8451-18d6309dc7c8"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
